                <head>Proclamation by the President</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>President Davis calls for a day of "fasting, humiliation and prayer" on
                    Friday, March 27, asking God to continue mercy toward the Confederate cause, to
                    scatter the enemy, and to restore peace and security.</summary>
                <note/>
